  "title": "Two round UFOs were spotted hovering over Curitiba-PR [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/01/two-round-ufos-were-spotted-hovering-over-curitiba-pr-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1oi",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUN 28th, 1994</strong>. Time: 15:30. Duration: 90 seconds. When he was close to the BR-116 highway, in the Pinheirinho region, Curitiba, State of Paraná, a man spotted two unidentified flying objects in the shape of balls; &#8220;two balls, one below, one above&#8221;. According to the witness, the objects were &#8220;half a meter each&#8221;, they were light in color and remained stationary, very close to each other, &#8220;glued&#8221;. The sighting was carried out with the naked eye and with good visibility conditions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.369. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado no Bairro Pinheirinho, Curitiba, Estado do Paraná</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
